<div class="comment">
<div class="meta"><a href="/project/LKML/list/?submitter=1141">Aneesh Kumar K.V</a> - Sept. 19, 2016, 5:50 a.m.</div>
<pre class="content">
Christophe Leroy &lt;christophe.leroy@c-s.fr&gt; writes:
<span class="quote">&gt; +#else</span>
<span class="quote">&gt; +static void hugepd_free(struct mmu_gather *tlb, void *hugepte)</span>
