<span class="quote">&gt; finding errors with that ?</span>

Having radix_enabled() being 0, it becomes:

if (!mmu_has_feature(MMU_FTR_16M_PAGE))
	return -ENODEV;

Which means hugepage will only be handled by CPUs having 16M pages. 
That&#39;s the issue.
